      "content": "it feels like everything is just gone. i used to look at a canvas and see a whole universe, but now i just see a blank white wall. it's like the part of me that actually lived, the part that mattered, just evaporated. i'm just sitting here in this body but there's nothing left inside. i feel like a hollow shell.",
