    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just what people say to make it feel better. therapy doesn't change the fact that the spark is dead. it's like... if a house is completely gutted by a fire, the walls are still there, but the home is gone. you're just staring at an empty structure. why does it even matter if the structure stays standing if nothing is happening inside it anymore?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
